Linux kernel
============

There are several guides for kernel developers and users. These guides can
be rendered in a number of formats, like HTML and PDF. Please read
Documentation/admin-guide/README.rst first.

In order to build the documentation, use ``make htmldocs`` or
``make pdfdocs``.  The formatted documentation can also be read online at:

    https://www.kernel.org/doc/html/latest/

There are various text files in the Documentation/ subdirectory,
several of them using the Restructured Text markup notation.

Please read the Documentation/process/changes.rst file, as it contains the
requirements for building and running the kernel, and information about
the problems which may result by upgrading your kernel.


# CCSDS协议开发模拟环境

## 编译工作环境
- 运行环境：Panda服务器的docker镜像, 镜像名字：`ccsds-kernel:6.6`
- 启动开发环境：
    ```
        docker run -dit \
            --name ccsds-protocol-dev \
            -v 本地用户开发代码路径:/root/data \
            -w /root \
            --add-host=host.docker.internal:host-gateway \
            -e http_proxy=http://host.docker.internal:7900 \
            -e https_proxy=http://host.docker.internal:7900 \
            --restart unless-stopped \
            ccsds-kernel:6.6
    ```
- 进入开发环境
    ```
        docker attach ccsds-protocol-dev        # 附加到已经运行的终端
        docker exec -it ccsds-dev /bin/bash     # 打开新的终端
    ```

## 代码实现
- 内核驱动代码位置：kernel-6-6/drivers/net/ccsds，其中包含驱动程序代码和测试代码

## 测试运行

1. 编译内核，内核模块
    ```
        make -j$(nproc)
        make dtbs
        make modules
    ```
2. 打包rootfs
    ```
        # 拷贝内核模块ccsds.ko 到 /root/data/rootfs/opt/ccsds_test
        cd /root/data/rootfs/
        cp ../kernel-6-6/drivers/net/ccsds/ccsds.ko opt/ccsds_test/
        find . | cpio -o --format=newc | gzip > ../rootfs.cpio.gz
    ```
3. 运行测试
    ```
        cd /root/data
        qemu-system-aarch64 \
            -machine virt \
            -cpu cortex-a57 \
            -m 2G \
            -nographic \
            -kernel /root/data/kernel-6-6/arch/arm64/boot/Image \
            -initrd /root/data/rootfs.cpio.gz \
            -append "console=ttyAMA0 rdinit=/sbin/init"
    ```
4. 执行测试
    ```
        cd /opt/ccsds_test/
        sh ccsds_test.sh
    ```

# 测试用例讲解

## Ping4的执行路径
```
 IPv4 ping 10.99.1.2
                                                                                                                                               
  ping 进程       
    │
    ▼  目的地 10.99.1.2 不是本机地址                                                                                                           
       路由表命中：10.99.1.0/24 dev ccsdsnet                                                                                                   
       → 出口网卡是 ccsdsnet，不走内核 loopback                                                                                                
    │                                                                                                                                          
    ▼  【经过驱动 TX】
    ccsds_ndo_start_xmit()                                                                                                                     
    → tx_fifo → ccsds_sim_echo 读走
    → 在用户态翻转 src/dst，改为 Echo Reply                                                                                                    
    │                                                                                                                                          
    ▼  【经过驱动 RX】                                                                                                                         
    sim_write() → rx_fifo → NAPI → napi_gro_receive()                                                                                          
    → IP 栈识别目的地 10.99.1.1（本机地址）
    → 投递给 ping 进程                                                                                                                         
   
  关键点：目的地 10.99.1.2 不是本机地址，内核不会走 loopback 快捷路径，强制走 ccsdsnet 出口。
```

## ping6的执行路径

```
IPv6 ping6 fd00::2
                                                                                                                                               
  ping6 进程
    │                                                                                                                                          
    ▼  路由命中：fd00::/64 dev ccsdsnet
    │
    ▼  【经过驱动 TX】NDP 阶段                                                                                                                 
    内核发 Neighbor Solicitation（询问 fd00::2 的链路层地址）
    → ndo_start_xmit → tx_fifo                                                                                                                 
    → ccsds_sim_echo 读走，handle_ipv6() 识别 ND_NEIGHBOR_SOLICIT                                                                              
    → 构造 Neighbor Advertisement 写回                                                                                                         
    【经过驱动 RX】→ rx_fifo → NAPI → IP 栈更新邻居表                                                                                          
    │                                                                                                                                          
    ▼  【经过驱动 TX】Echo Request
    ndo_start_xmit → tx_fifo                                                                                                                   
    → ccsds_sim_echo 读走，识别 ICMP6_ECHO_REQUEST
    → 翻转地址，改为 Echo Reply，重算 ICMPv6 checksum
    【经过驱动 RX】→ rx_fifo → NAPI → IP 栈 → ping6 进程
```




